text: The ferry MS Sewol, travelling from Incheon towards Jeju Island off the south coast of South Korea, sank on April 16, 2014 near Jindo Island off the southwest coast, resulting in the death of 304 people. ==References== Category:2014 disasters Category:2014 in Asia Category:2010s disasters in Asia Category:2010s in South Korea Category:April 2014 events Category:Shipwrecks Category:Transport in South Korea
